Testabdeckung für die drei kritischsten Module:

badge_security_test.dart (44 Tests):
  - Pubkey/Signatur-Validierung (Hex-Format, Länge)
  - JSON-Kanonisierung (deterministisch)
  - Legacy v1 Deaktivierung (Security Audit C1)
  - Schnorr-Signatur: Sign → Verify Roundtrip
  - Manipulation Detection (Meetup, Block, Pubkey, Sig)
  - Cross-Signing-Schutz
  - Ablauf-Checks (isExpired, expiryInfo)
  - Unified verify() Routing (Kompakt vs Legacy)
  - Normalisierung (Compact → Full Format)
  - QR Legacy Ablehnung

trust_score_test.dart (26 Tests):
  - Bootstrap-Phasen (Keimphase/Wachstum/Stabil)
  - Score-Berechnung (Maturity, Diversity, Activity, Decay)
  - Frequency Cap (max 2 Badges/Woche)
  - Promotion-Schwellenwerte
  - Bridge Score (Cross-Meetup-Vernetzung)
  - Sybil-Erkennung (Single-Signer, Same-Day)
  - TrustScore Level/DisplayScore Zuordnung
  - TrustConfig Konstanten-Validierung

badge_model_test.dart (34 Tests):
  - toJson/fromJson Roundtrip (inkl. Backward-Compatibility)
  - Krypto-Properties (hasCryptoProof, isNostrSigned)
  - Claim-Binding (isClaimed, isFullyBound)
  - withClaim() Builder (Immutability)
  - proofId / claimProofId Deterministik
  - Badge-Proof-Hash (v1 + v2, Sortierung)
  - verifyBadgeProof
  - Reputations-Statistiken

Ausführen: flutter test
